<L>__{interior northern tunnel day}
<A>__{blade and reinhardt trudge along. the tunnel slopes inward, forming a v shaped channel where a trickle of water flows. blade notices something bobbing in the water. he nudges it with his foot and knocks it free. it's a broken human tibia which twirls around, then flows past their legs. a few steps later on, reinhardt notices something else. he stoops into waist deep water, picking up what he thinks is an isolated human rib but ends up snagging a tangled mass of hair, mud, and bones.}
